                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7406" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1162</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3559 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赤峰环保子基金：沉舟侧畔千帆过，政府引导基金的创新投资之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Chifeng Environmental Protection Sub Fund：A Thousand Sails Pass by The Side of The Sunken Boat，Innovative Investment Path of Government Guide Fund</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">谢晓燕、刘洪杨（通讯作者）、兰宇翔、周艳明</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宁波梅山保税港区膜天君富投资管理有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">股权投资基金；政府引导基金；基金募资；基金投后管理；基金退出；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Equity investment fund; Government guiding fund; Fundraising; Post investment management of funds; Fund withdrawal</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在我国社会主义市场经济快速发展背景下，经济结构不断转型升级，股权投资基金得以飞速发展，尤其政府引导基金是政府招商及投资引导最重要的抓手，重点涵盖基础设施投资、产业招商、资本市场引导投资等各个方向。本案例讲述了以内蒙环保母基金和赤峰政府引导基金两只省域与区域基金以创新模式互相募资成立赤峰环保子基金（管理人为膜天君富），按照“募、投、管、退”四大基金标准运作投资众城环卫公司（敖汉旗环卫项目）的整个过程。子基金采用股权投资模式，运用绝对估值法对众城环卫进行估值，并创新性引入两家战略投资者，其中一家专业的环卫公司保障了未来项目运营成功；另外一家为环保母基金出资人控股的国有环保公司，子基金将所投公司控制管理权授权给同一控制下的这家公司，对于子基金的投后管理，以及安全退出提供了一定保障。在近几年政府引导基金运作过程中各种问题层出不穷的背景下，该子基金管理人新颖的募资方式、以及通过联合体的创新性股权设计以确保基金投后管理及退出的安全，为政府引导基金这一类的私募股权投资基金提供了一定的借鉴作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the rapid development of China&#39;s socialist market economy, equity investment funds have developed rapidly, especially the government guidance fund is the most important starting point of investment guidance. This case describes the whole process of setting up Chifeng environmental protection sub fund with Inner Mongolia Environmental Protection FOF and Chifeng government guidance fund, which are matched with each other, and investing in Zhongcheng company according to the four links of &quot;raising, investing, managing and withdrawing&quot;. The fund-raising method of setting up sub funds through mutual allocation between the two guiding funds is novel. The sub fund adopts the equity investment mode and uses the absolute valuation method to value the company. In the equity investment in Zhongcheng sanitation investment, two strategic investors are innovatively introduced, and one professional sanitation company ensures the successful operation of the project; Another is a state-owned environmental protection company under the same control of the environmental protection FOF. The sub fund authorizes the control and management right of the invested company to this company, which ensures the post investment safety and exit safety of the sub fund. Under the background of imperfect operation of government guidance fund, the novel fund-raising method of the sub fund and innovative design to ensure post investment management and exit safety provide a certain reference for PE investment funds such as government guidance fund.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司财务》、《投资学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">协同效应理论；公司治理理论；风险管理理论；资源依赖理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-08</td>
                            </tr>
